		<h4>Logic Flows</h4>
		<p>For checkout, I then started to map out the possible logic flows for our new experience.  My two recommendations were (1) a simple one-page checkout and (2) a simple serialized flow.</p>
		<p>I also worked on a system for classifying errors. I bucketed the errors into three main types, and designed the interaction for each.</p>
	</div>
